        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            


<p><placeName>Alexandria </placeName><date when="1823-12-01">Decr 1st 1823</date></p>
<p>Dr Sir,</p>

<p>The <persName>bearer </persName><persName>Mr John Hall</persName> desiring to go into your part of the
country has requested of me a letter. <persName>Mr Hall</persName> is a man of 
respectable parentage and connexion in this <placeName>parish</placeName>&#8212;and is himself so far
as I am acquainted with him a man of respectability and enterprise.</p>

<p><persName>J. Thomas</persName></p>
<p><persName>Hon Stephen F. Austin</persName></p>

        </div1>
